vmwVcopsMIB.name: vmwVcopsMIB

revisions.description: Rewrite Integrien MIB for Alive v7.0 aka 'Carbon'

vmwVcopsMIB.contactinfo: VMware, Inc 3401 Hillview Ave Palo Alto, CA 94304 Tel: 1-877-486-9273 or 650-427-5000 Fax: 650-427-5001 Web: http://communities.vmware.com/community/developer/forums/managementapi
vmwVcopsMIB.description: This MIB file contains the information that the receiving party needs in order to interpret the SNMP traps sent by vCenter Operations Manager.

vmwareAlertTrap.name: vmwareAlertTrap
vmwareAlertTrap.description: This group is actually the prefix one uses when creating enterprise-specific trap OID's for an SNMPv2 trap. It is used in the VMware MIB when defining traps.

vmwareGenericAlertData.name: vmwareGenericAlertData
vmwareGenericAlertData.description: This members of this group are the OIDs for VarBinds that contain data for ALL Alerts.

vmwareAlertAliveServerName.name: vmwareAlertAliveServerName
vmwareAlertAliveServerName.description: The name of the VCOPs server that generated this alert.

vmwareAlertEntityName.name: vmwareAlertEntityName
vmwareAlertEntityName.description: The Entity name about which this alert was generated.

vmwareAlertEntityType.name: vmwareAlertEntityType
vmwareAlertEntityType.description: The Entity type about which this alert was generated.

vmwareAlertTimestamp.name: vmwareAlertTimestamp
vmwareAlertTimestamp.description: The timestamp of the alert in UTC format.

vmwareAlertCriticality.name: vmwareAlertCriticality
vmwareAlertCriticality.description: A text string describing the alert criticality level.

vmwareAlertRootCause.name: vmwareAlertRootCause
vmwareAlertRootCause.description: A text string describing the root-cause of the alert that was generated.

vmwareAlertURL.name: vmwareAlertURL
vmwareAlertURL.description: The URL of the 'Alert Summary' page of the alert that was generated.

vmwareAlertID.name: vmwareAlertID
vmwareAlertID.description: The unique VCOPs identifier of the alert that was generated.

vmwareAlertMessage.name: vmwareAlertMessage
vmwareAlertMessage.description: The info message of the alert that was generated.

vmwareAlertType.name: vmwareAlertType
vmwareAlertType.description: The textual type description of the alert that was generated.

vmwareAlertSubtype.name: vmwareAlertSubtype
vmwareAlertSubtype.description: The textual subtype description of the alert that was generated.

vmwareTrapKPIPredictionChange.description: A trap describing a Smart Alert that predicts a KPI Breach condition (also know as 'Fingerprint') that experiences a change in one or more of the following values: - Prediction probability - Prediction projected time - Prediction reason.
